## Infrastructure and Development Rules
- use bun for node commands
- use Docker for containerization and consistent environments
- implement proper environment variable management
- use .env files for local development
- implement proper logging and monitoring
- use health checks for all services
- implement proper error handling and graceful degradation
- use semantic versioning for releases
- implement proper CI/CD pipelines
- use linting and formatting tools (ESLint, Prettier)
- implement proper security practices (HTTPS, CORS, etc.)
- use proper resource limits and monitoring
- implement proper backup and disaster recovery procedures
- use infrastructure as code when possible
- implement proper testing strategies (unit, integration, e2e)
